text: What's So Bad About Feeling Good? is a 1968 American comedy movie directed by George Seaton and starring George Peppard, Mary Tyler Moore, Dom DeLuise, John McMartin, Charles Lane, Thelma Ritter. It was distributed by Universal Pictures and was a box office disappoint. ==Other websites== * Category:1968 comedy movies Category:1968 fantasy movies Category:American fantasy movies Category:American comedy movies Category:Movies directed by George Seaton
